Absa Group Buys South African Islamic Insurer Takafol, Business Day Says

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-09-09T04:39:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/absa-group-buys-south-african-islamic-insurer-takafol-business-day-says.html
Absa Group Ltd. (ASA)  bought Takafol  South
Africa  Ltd., the country’s only provider of Islamic insurance,
for an undisclosed sum, Business Day said, citing Absa Islamic
Banking Managing Director Amman Muhammad.  Takafol was started in 2003 and wiill be rebranded Absa
Takafol, the Johannesburg-based newspaper said. South Africa’s
Islamic insurance market collects about 3 billion rand in annual
premiums, Business Day said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  